        <h1>Financial Management System (FMS)</h1>

        <h2>Project Overview</h2>
        <p>This project aims to develop a Financial Management System focusing on managing the Chart of Accounts (COA) and Journal Entries (JEs) with robust features.</p>

        <h2>Key Features</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>CRUD operations for COA and JEs</li>
            <li>Fluent validations</li>
            <li>API-based structure with JWT authentication</li>
            <li>Clean Architecture with CQRS and generic repository pattern</li>
            <li>Pagination on listings</li>
            <li>Reporting using jQuery DataTable</li>
            <li>Database management with SQL Server 2022</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Technical Stack</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Backend: .NET 4.8 (C#)</li>
            <li>Frontend: jQuery</li>
            <li>Database: SQL Server 2022</li>
            <li>Authentication: JWT</li>
        </ul>        

        <h2>Conclusion</h2>
        <p>The FMS project will provide an efficient solution for financial data management through a modern API-driven architecture.</p>

